and make a combustible gas in a test tube. You can then hold it over a candle flame and see as well as hear the exciting &#34;whoosh!&#34; as combustible hydrogen combines with oxygen in the air. The well-written manual that comes with this kit explains how hydrogen collects solar power and can also be used in cells that can power a number of things, including vehicles."]},"id":"162168aa-e2cf-4c0b-aee3-6695f03c551c","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Chemicals"},"id":"d82bede6-ea4a-4ff4-bfb0-7b87269c79ad","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/4PJxC2ARpxJJG9GNFdtN5E.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The C2000 comes with specialized chemicals such as potassium hexacyanoferrate (II) and ammonium iron (III) sulfate, as well as household chemicals such as baking soda. There are 18 chemicals in the kit. Additional chemicals are required to complete some of the experiments, including some you can buy at grocery or hardware stores and some you need to get from a science store such as Best Science Supplies. The kit includes a sufficient supply of chemicals to conduct the experiments more than once.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/49704-chem-c20003.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/4PJxC2ARpxJJG9GNFdtN5E.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"4PJxC2ARpxJJG9GNFdtN5E","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/4PJxC2ARpxJJG9GNFdtN5E.jpg","alt":""},"id":"0d2edf3b-4c23-4470-bd32-c767231fdb1d","type":"image"},{"data":{"text":"Learning Materials"},"id":"867598b0-4b72-43fc-8338-c20e749122d3","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Like all the kits on our lineup, the CHEM C2000 comes with an experiment procedure manual that includes detailed explanations of the principles behind the experiments. Because the C2000 is a fairly advanced kit, the manual may be a bit too complex for kids under 10 to follow. This kit is designed for users who already have a basic grasp of chemistry and experimental procedures."]},"id"